B lc Kalman

By Evgenia "Jenny" Nitishinskaya, Dr. Aidan O'Mahony, and Delaney Granizo-Mackenzie. Algorithms by David Edwards.

Kalman Filter Beta Estimation Example from Dr. Aidan O'Mahony's blog.

Edited by AI Cafe

Kalman filter l mt thut ton s dng cc quan st nhiu ca mt h thng theo thi gian c lng cc tham s ca h thng (mt s trong s khng th quan st c) v d on cc quan st trong tng lai. Ti mi bc thi gian, n a ra mt d on, nhn mt php o v cp nht bn thn da trn s so snh gia d on v php o.

Thut ton c thc hin nh sau:

  1. Nhn u vo mt m hnh ton hc ca h thng, tc l:
    • ma trn chuyn tip, cho bit cch h thng tin trin t trng thi ny sang trng thi khc. V d, nu chng ta ang m phng chuyn ng ca mt chic xe, th cc gi tr tip theo ca v tr v vn tc c th c tnh ton t cc gi tr trc bng cch s dng cc phng trnh ng hc. Hoc, nu chng ta c mt h thng tng i n nh, chng ta c th m hnh ha s tin trin ca n nh mt chuyn ng ngu nhin. Nu bn mun tm hiu v cc b lc Kalman, hy lu rng ma trn ny thng c gi l $A$.
    • ma trn quan st, cho bit php o tip theo m chng ta nn mong i da trn trng thi d on tip theo. Nu chng ta ang o v tr ca chic xe, chng ta ch cn trch xut cc gi tr v tr c lu trong trng thi. V d phc tp hn, hy xem xt vic c lng mt m hnh hi quy tuyn tnh cho d liu. Khi , trng thi ca chng ta l cc h s ca m hnh, v chng ta c th d on php o tip theo t phng trnh tuyn tnh. iu ny c k hiu l $H$.
    • bt k yu t kim sot no nh hng n cc chuyn tip trng thi nhng khng phi l mt phn ca cc php o. V d, nu chic xe ca chng ta ang ri, trng lc s l mt yu t kim sot. Nu nhiu khng c trung bnh bng 0, n nn c dch chuyn v lch c a vo cc yu t kim sot. Cc yu t kim sot c tm tt trong mt ma trn $B$ vi vector kim sot thay i theo thi gian $u_t$, cung cp lch $Bu_t$.
    • ma trn hip phng sai ca nhiu chuyn tip (tc l nhiu trong s tin trin ca h thng) v nhiu o, c k hiu l $Q$ v $R$, tng ng.
  2. Nhn u vo mt c lng ban u ca trng thi ca h thng v sai s ca c lng, $\mu_0$ v $\sigma_0$.
  3. Ti mi bc:
    • c lng trng thi hin ti ca h thng $x_t$ s dng ma trn chuyn tip
    • nhn cc php o mi $z_t$
    • s dng xc sut c iu kin ca cc php o da trn trng thi, lu n nhng bt nh ca php o v c lng trng thi, cp nht trng thi hin ti c tnh ca h thng $x_t$ v ma trn hip phng sai ca c lng $P_t$.

Hnh nh ny minh ha quy trnh m thut ton thc hin.

thut ton theo di cc hip phng sai ca cc c lng ca n l rt quan trng. Bng cch ny, n c th a ra mt kt qu tinh vi hn l ch mt gi tr im khi chng ta yu cu n, v n c th s dng s t tin ca mnh quyt nh mc b nh hng bi cc php o mi trong qu trnh cp nht. Cng chc chn v c lng ca n v trng thi, n s cng hoi nghi v cc php o khng ng vi trng thi.

Mc nh, cc sai s c gi nh l phn phi chun, v gi nh ny cho php thut ton tnh ton cc khong tin cy chnh xc. Tuy nhin, n c th c thc hin cho cc sai s khng chun.

V d: qu bng ri

Hy tng tng rng chng ta c mt qu bng ang ri m chuyn ng ca n c theo di bng mt camera. Trng thi ca qu bng bao gm v tr v vn tc ca n. Chng ta bit rng chng ta c mi quan h $x_t = x_{t-1} + v_{t-1}\tau - \frac{1}{2} g \tau^2$, trong $\tau$ l thi gian (tnh bng giy) tri qua gia $t-1$ v $t$, v $g$ l gia tc trng trng. Trong khi , camera ca chng ta c th cho chng ta bit v tr ca qu bng mi giy, nhng chng ta bit t nh sn xut rng chnh xc ca camera, c chuyn thnh v tr ca qu bng, c bin thin trong c lng v tr khong 3 mt.

s dng b lc Kalman, chng ta cn cung cp cho n cc ma trn chuyn tip v quan st, cc ma trn hip phng sai chuyn tip v quan st, cng nh trng thi ban u. Trng thi ca h thng l (v tr, vn tc), v vy n tun theo ma trn chuyn tip $$ \left( \begin{array}{cc} 1 & \tau \\ 0 & 1 \end{array} \right) $$

vi lch $(-\tau^2 \cdot g/2, -\tau\cdot g)$. Ma trn quan st ch trch xut ta v tr, (1 0), v chng ta ang o v tr. Chng ta bit rng bin thin quan st l 1, v hip phng sai chuyn tip l 0 v chng ta s m phng d liu theo cch m chng ta ch nh m hnh ca mnh. i vi trng thi ban u, hy cung cp cho m hnh ca chng ta mt ci g gi mo nh (30, 10) v xem h thng ca chng ta tin trin nh th no.

In[3]:
tau = 0.1

# Set up the filter
kf = KalmanFilter(n_dim_obs=1, n_dim_state=2, # position is 1-dimensional, (x,v) is 2-dimensional
                  initial_state_mean=[30,10],
                  initial_state_covariance=np.eye(2),
                  transition_matrices=[[1,tau], [0,1]],
                  observation_matrices=[[1,0]],
                  observation_covariance=3,
                  transition_covariance=np.zeros((2,2)),
                  transition_offsets=[-4.9*tau**2, -9.8*tau])
In[4]:
# Create a simulation of a ball falling for 40 units of time (each of length tau)
times = np.arange(40)
actual = -4.9*tau**2*times**2

# Simulate the noisy camera data
sim = actual + 3*np.random.randn(40)

# Run filter on camera data
state_means, state_covs = kf.filter(sim)
In[5]:
plt.plot(times, state_means[:,0])
plt.plot(times, sim)
plt.plot(times, actual)
plt.legend(['Filter estimate', 'Camera data', 'Actual'])
plt.xlabel('Time')
plt.ylabel('Height');

Ti mi thi im, chng ta v c lng trng thi sau khi tnh n php o gn y nht, l l do ti sao chng ta khng v tr 30 vo thi im 0. S ch ca b lc i vi cc php o cho php n iu chnh cho trng thi ban u khng chnh xc m chng ta cung cp. Sau , bng cch nh gi m hnh ca n v kin thc v cc quy lut vt l so vi cc php o mi, n c kh nng lc ra phn ln nhiu trong d liu t camera. Trong khi , tin cy vo c lng tng ln theo thi gian, nh c th hin trong biu di y:

B lc Kalman cng c th thc hin lm mt, iu ny c ngha l n tip nhn tt c d liu u vo cng mt lc v sau xy dng c lng tt nht cho trng thi ca h thng trong mi khong thi gian sau ny. Tc l, n khng cung cp c lng trc tuyn, m thay vo s dng tt c d liu c lng trng thi lch s, iu ny rt hu ch nu chng ta ch mun s dng d liu sau khi thu thp tt c.

V d: trung bnh ng

V b lc Kalman cp nht c lng ca n ti mi bc thi gian v c xu hng cn nhc cc quan st gn y hn l cc quan st c hn, mt ng dng c bit hu ch l c lng cc tham s ng ca d liu. Khi s dng b lc Kalman, khng c di ca s no m chng ta cn ch nh. iu ny rt hu ch cho vic tnh ton trung bnh ng nu l iu chng ta quan tm, hoc lm mt cc c lng ca cc i lng khc. Chng hn, nu chng ta tnh ton t l Sharpe ng, chng ta c th lm mt n bng cch s dng b lc Kalman.

Di y, chng ta s s dng c b lc Kalman v trung bnh ng n ngy c lng trung bnh ng ca mt tp d liu. Chng ta hy vng rng trung bnh m t tt cc quan st ca chng ta, v vy n khng nn thay i qu nhiu khi chng ta thm mt quan st; do , chng ta gi nh rng n pht trin nh mt bc i ngu nhin vi mt sai s nh. Trung bnh l d on ca m hnh cho trung bnh ca phn phi t cc php o c ly ra, v vy d on ca chng ta cho gi tr tip theo n gin bng vi c lng ca chng ta v trung bnh. Chng ta gi nh rng cc quan st c phng sai 1 xung quanh trung bnh ng, v khng c c lng tt hn. D on ban u ca chng ta cho trung bnh l 0, nhng b lc nhanh chng nhn ra rng iu l sai v iu chnh.

In[9]:
from data import get_prices

start = '2023-01-01'
end = '2025-01-01'

x = get_prices('FPT', start_date=start, end_date=end).FPT

# Construct a Kalman filter
kf = KalmanFilter(transition_matrices = [1],
                  observation_matrices = [1],
                  initial_state_mean = 0,
                  initial_state_covariance = 1,
                  observation_covariance=1,
                  transition_covariance=.01)

# Use the observed values of the price to get a rolling mean
state_means, _ = kf.filter(x.values)
state_means = pd.Series(state_means.flatten(), index=x.index)

# Compute the rolling mean with various lookback windows
mean30 = x.rolling(window = 30).mean()
mean60 = x.rolling(window = 60).mean()
mean90 = x.rolling(window = 90).mean()

# Plot original data and estimated mean
plt.plot(state_means)
plt.plot(x)
plt.plot(mean30)
plt.plot(mean60)
plt.plot(mean90)
plt.title('Kalman filter estimate of average')
plt.legend(['Kalman Estimate', 'X', '30-day Moving Average', '60-day Moving Average','90-day Moving Average'])
plt.xlabel('Day')
plt.ylabel('Price');

iu ny hi kh nhn, v vy chng ta s v mt phn ca th.

Li th ca b lc Kalman l chng ta khng cn phi chn chiu di ca s, do chng ta gp t ri ro hn trong vic qu khp (overfitting). Tuy nhin, chng ta vn c th gp phi vn qu khp vi mt s tham s khi to cho b lc, nhng nhng tham s d dng c xc nh mt cch khch quan hn. Chng ta khng th loi b hon ton vic qu khp, nhng b lc Kalman chnh xc hn so vi trung bnh ng v thng th tt hn.

V d: hi quy tuyn tnh

Hy th s dng b lc Kalman tm cc ng hi quy tuyn tnh cho mt tp d liu. Chng ta s so snh gi c phiu vi ch s VNINDEX, v vy kt qu s l mt loi alpha v beta lin tc cho c phiu, trong $\alpha$ v $\beta$ l cc tham s ca phng trnh hi quy tuyn tnh $$ y_t \approx \alpha + \beta x_t $$

Di y, chng ta s dng mu sc ch ra cc ngy m cc im d liu $(x_t, y_t)$ tng ng.

In[11]:
# Load pricing data

start = '2022-01-01'
end = '2025-01-01'

prices = get_prices('FPT', 'VNINDEX', start_date=start, end_date=end).ffill()

y = prices['FPT']
x = prices['VNINDEX']
In[12]:
# Plot data and use colormap to indicate the date each point corresponds to
cm = plt.get_cmap('jet')
colors = np.linspace(0.1, 1, len(x))
sc = plt.scatter(x, y, s=30, c=colors, cmap=cm, edgecolor='k', alpha=0.7)

plt.ylabel('FPT');

Hy cng tm hiu cc u vo cho b lc Kalman ca chng ta. Chng ta s ni rng trng thi ca h thng ca chng ta l ng thng m cc quan st ang theo, vi cc tham s $\alpha$ v $\beta$. D on ban u ca chng ta cho cc tham s ny l (0,0), vi ma trn hip phng sai (m t sai s ca d on ca chng ta) l tt c cc gi tr bng mt. Nh trong v d v trung bnh ng, chng ta gi nh rng cc tham s ca chng ta theo mt bc i ngu nhin (ma trn chuyn tip l ma trn n v) vi mt hng mc sai s nh (hip phng sai chuyn tip l mt s nh nhn vi ma trn n v).

chuyn t trng thi ca h thng sang mt quan st, chng ta nhn im trng thi $(\beta, \alpha)$ vi $(x_i, 1)$ c $\beta x_i + \alpha \approx y_i$, v vy ma trn quan st ca chng ta ch l mt ct ca cc s 1 gn lin vi $x$. Chng ta gi nh rng phng sai ca cc quan st $y$ l 2. By gi chng ta sn sng s dng cc quan st ca $y$ pht trin cc c lng ca cc tham s $\alpha$ v $\beta$.

In[13]:
delta = 1e-3
trans_cov = delta / (1 - delta) * np.eye(2) # How much random walk wiggles
obs_mat = np.expand_dims(np.vstack([[x], [np.ones(len(x))]]).T, axis=1)

kf = KalmanFilter(n_dim_obs=1, n_dim_state=2, # y is 1-dimensional, (alpha, beta) is 2-dimensional
                  initial_state_mean=[0,0],
                  initial_state_covariance=np.ones((2, 2)),
                  transition_matrices=np.eye(2),
                  observation_matrices=obs_mat,
                  observation_covariance=2,
                  transition_covariance=trans_cov)
In[14]:
# Use the observations y to get running estimates and errors for the state parameters
state_means, state_covs = kf.filter(y.values)

Di y, chng ta v biu cc gi tr trung bnh - tc l, c lng tt nht ca chng ta - v $\alpha$ v $\beta$ theo thi gian.

Lu rng cc tham s dao ng nhiu qua cc khong thi gian di. Nu chng ta da vo mt thut ton giao dch da trn iu ny, chng hn nh mt ci g lin quan n vic phng h beta, th vic c c c lng tt nht v cp nht nht v beta l rt quan trng. hnh dung cch m h thng tin trin theo thi gian, chng ti v biu mi trng thi th nm (m hnh tuyn tnh) bn di. so snh, mu en l ng c tr v bng cch s dng hi quy bnh phng nh nht trn ton b tp d liu, iu ny rt khc bit.

In[16]:
# Plot data points using colormap
sc = plt.scatter(x, y, s=30, c=colors, cmap=cm, edgecolor='k', alpha=0.7)
cb = plt.colorbar(sc)
cb.ax.yaxis.set_major_locator(mpl.ticker.FixedLocator(cb.ax.get_yticks().tolist()))

# Plot every fifth line
step = 5
xi = np.linspace(x.min()-5, x.max()+5, 2)
colors_l = np.linspace(0.1, 1, len(state_means[::step]))
for i, beta in enumerate(state_means[::step]):
    plt.plot(xi, beta[0] * xi + beta[1], alpha=.2, lw=1, c=cm(colors_l[i]))

# Plot the OLS regression line
plt.plot(xi, poly1d(np.polyfit(x, y, 1))(xi), '0.4')

# Label axes
plt.xlabel('VNINDEX')
plt.ylabel('FPT');

Lu rng mc d tt c cc c lng trng thi u xem xt tt c cc quan st trc , nhng chng ph hp vi d liu gn y hn l d liu c. iu ny cho php b lc thch ng vi cc thay i cu trc trong d liu theo thi gian.

By gi, phn ln thi gian chng ta quan tm n s tng quan trong li nhun nhiu hn l s tng quan trong gi c, v vy hy nhanh chng s dng cng mt cu trc hi quy tuyn tnh trn d liu li nhun:

In[17]:
# Get returns from pricing data
x_r = x.pct_change()[1:]
y_r = y.pct_change()[1:]

# Run Kalman filter on returns data
delta_r = 1e-2
trans_cov_r = delta_r / (1 - delta_r) * np.eye(2) # How much random walk wiggles
obs_mat_r = np.expand_dims(np.vstack([[x_r], [np.ones(len(x_r))]]).T, axis=1)
kf_r = KalmanFilter(n_dim_obs=1, n_dim_state=2, # y_r is 1-dimensional, (alpha, beta) is 2-dimensional
                  initial_state_mean=[0,0],
                  initial_state_covariance=np.ones((2, 2)),
                  transition_matrices=np.eye(2),
                  observation_matrices=obs_mat_r,
                  observation_covariance=.01,
                  transition_covariance=trans_cov_r)
state_means_r, _ = kf_r.filter(y_r.values)

# Plot data points using colormap
colors_r = np.linspace(0.1, 1, len(x_r))
sc = plt.scatter(x_r, y_r, s=30, c=colors_r, cmap=cm, edgecolor='k', alpha=0.7)
cb = plt.colorbar(sc)
cb.ax.yaxis.set_major_locator(mpl.ticker.FixedLocator(cb.ax.get_yticks().tolist()))

# Plot every fifth line
step = 5
xi = np.linspace(x_r.min()-4, x_r.max()+4, 2)
colors_l = np.linspace(0.1, 1, len(state_means_r[::step]))
for i, beta in enumerate(state_means_r[::step]):
    plt.plot(xi, beta[0] * xi + beta[1], alpha=.2, lw=1, c=cm(colors_l[i]))

# Plot the OLS regression line
plt.plot(xi, poly1d(np.polyfit(x_r, y_r, 1))(xi), '0.4')

# Adjust axes for visibility
plt.axis([-0.03,0.03,-0.11, 0.11])

# Label axes
plt.xlabel('VNINDEX returns')
plt.ylabel('FPT returns');

Mc d d liu th y b ri rm hn nhiu, nhng chng ta c th thy ng hi quy ang pht trin, thm ch c lc vt qua ng hi quy OLS.

Tng qut

Chng ta c th s dng b lc Kalman m hnh ha cc hm chuyn tip v quan st phi tuyn. lm iu ny, c cc b lc Kalman m rng v c chn lc (unscented), trong b lc unscented c bao gm trong pykalman. Nhng b lc ny thm ch c th m hnh ha cc tnh hung m nhiu khng phi l cng dn (v d, ni nhiu t l vi kch thc ca php o). Chng ta cng c th ch nh cc li phi Gauss; iu ny rt hu ch trong d liu ti chnh, thng c phn phi ui nng.

Ngoi ra cn c cc thut ton suy din mt s tham s u vo, chng hn nh ma trn hip phng sai v trng thi ban u, t mt tp d liu ban u. iu ny c th c thc hin vi phng thc pykalman.em().

Lu : Ti liu ny mang tnh cht chia s kin thc khoa hc d liu. Cc m chng khon xut hin trong ti liu ch mang tnh cht minh ho, khng khuyn ngh u t. Chng ti khng chu trch nhim trc mi ri ro no do s dng ti liu ny.
